A '''fruit plantation''' is a primary industry that only appears in the [[Main/en/sub-tropical climate]]. It produces [[Main/en/fruit]] which should be delivered to a [[Main/en/food processing plant]], but does not accept any cargo. Fruit plantations can only be built in grassy non-desert areas.

